    <item>
      <title>马来西亚考虑恢复消费税以刺激财政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/malaysia-weighs-bringing-back-consumption-tax-to-boost-finances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，马来西亚政府正考虑恢复广泛的消费税，而不是削减常用汽油的补贴，以增强财政实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/malaysia-weighs-bringing-back-consumption-tax-to-boost-finances</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 09:51:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>死于 Mpox 的儿童并不是第一批接种疫苗的人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/mpox-outbreak-children-in-congo-are-far-from-first-in-line-for-a-vaccine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在刚果民主共和国，儿童占了麻疹死亡人数的 80% 以上，但该国首批抵达的疫苗却不会给最年幼、最脆弱的患者接种。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/mpox-outbreak-children-in-congo-are-far-from-first-in-line-for-a-vaccine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 07:54:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
